text.text: The rougamo was crispy and light, with pork filling that's flavourful and not too salty. Great for a light meal. HK milk tea is pretty average and comes without sugar, so I had to add a couple of packets of white sugar to sweeten it. I liked the fast food style seating, and the overall restaurant was clean and comfortable.
